ss. No matter what strategies you devise, they will be translated into logical series of actions. These action responses will prove to be highly beneficial in achieving your goal, which happens to be the resumption and recovery of your business venture.","position":{"start":{"line":221,"column":1,"offset":5084},"end":{"line":221,"column":384,"offset":5467},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":221,"column":1,"offset":5084},"end":{"line":221,"column":384,"offset":5467},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"Let’s get down to finding how these strategies work. Suppose, you choose to make your staff work from their homes, in response to a severe calamity such as winter storms. The below table will offer you a gamut of response steps worth taking in this context.","position":{"start":{"line":223,"column":1,"offset":5469},"end":{"line":223,"column":258,"offset":5726},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":223,"column":1,"offset":5469},"end":{"line":223,"column":258,"offset":5726},"indent":[]}},{"type":"html","value":"<table width=\"877\" style=\"height: 578px;\" >\n<tbody >\n<tr >","position":{"start":{"line":224,"column":1,"offset":5727},"end":{"line":226,"column":6,"offset":5785},"indent":[1,1]}},{"type":"html","value":"<td width=\"501\" >a.     Monitoring the weather reports and updates on the winter storm.","position":{"start":{"line":228,"column":1,"offset":5787},"end":{"line":228,"column":88,"offset":5874},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"b.    Monitoring status of highways as well as public transports.","position":{"start":{"line":230,"column":1,"offset":5876},"end":{"line":230,"column":66,"offset":5941},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":230,"column":1,"offset":5876},"end":{"line":230,"column":66,"offset":5941},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"c.     Emergency response teams must find out the exact conditions, by conducting periodic conference calls.","position":{"start":{"line":232,"column":1,"offset":5943},"end":{"line":232,"column":109,"offset":6051},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":232,"column":1,"offset":5943},"end":{"line":232,"column":109,"offset":6051},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"d.    Create and send messages to the entire workforce, asking them to work from home. You must also call their supervisors immediately.","position":{"start":{"line":234,"column":1,"offset":6053},"end":{"line":234,"column":137,"offset":6189},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":234,"column":1,"offset":6053},"end":{"line":234,"column":137,"offset":6189},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"e.     Under the assumption that commuting will be risky, the emergency team asks staff to work from home.","position":{"start":{"line":236,"column":1,"offset":6191},"end":{"line":236,"column":107,"offset":6297},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":236,"column":1,"offset":6191},"end":{"line":236,"column":107,"offset":6297},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"f.      The emergency team also enquires about the availability of resources from IT workforces, thus ensuring they have sufficient resources as well as remote network support for employees working from homes.","position":{"start":{"line":238,"column":1,"offset":6299},"end":{"line":238,"column":210,"offset":6508},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":238,"column":1,"offset":6299},"end":{"line":238,"column":210,"offset":6508},"indent":[]}},{"type":"paragraph","children":[{"type":"text","value":"g.     Based on the assumptions that resources can be arranged for within short time, emergency team suggests working from home.","position":{"start":{"line":240,"column":1,"offset":6510},"end":{"line":240,"column":129,"offset":6638},"indent":[]}}],"position":{"start":{"line":240,"column":1,"offset":6510},"end":{"line":240,"column":129,"offset":6638},"indent":